		{
			"id": "title",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# UC2 · PII Redaction — Request DAG\nPresidio flags `EMAIL_ADDRESS HIGH`. Sanitize replaces the span. Backend receives redacted payload. `action = redact`, `blocked = false`.",
